  ¡§Toa7--e5 kio3 Chhai2-giok8, se3--e5 kio3 Chhai2-song.¡¨ Khi2 hoan3-chhu3 e5 Lim5 chu2-jim7 khok8-khok8 haiN3-thau5: ¡§Sit8-chai7 chin khou2-lian5, chu7 se3-han3 a-bu2 to7 lai5 li7-khui....¡¨ ¡§In ma-ma...?¡¨ ¡§Aih, kong2--khi2-lai5 oe7 tng5, hit-chun7 goa2 chiah lai5 kong-si bo5 joa7 ku2.¡¨ Peng5-si5 ai3 kong2 chhio3 e5 Lim5 chu2-jim7, kong2-tioh8 chiaN5 kam2-seng3: ¡§In ma-ma goa2 khoaN3-koe3 nng7-pai2, than2-peh8 kong2 sui2 koh u7 lang5-ian5, sui-jian5 si7 chng-kha-lang5, chit8-sut-a2 to boe7 song5, kho2-sioh Kheng3-tong5 bo5 hok-khi3 khi3 hou7 chau2--khi3.¡¨ KhoaN3 A-eng gi5-bun7 teng5-teng5, sui5 soa3 loh8-khi3 kong2: ¡§Kheng3-tong5 goan2 long2 kio3 ou-to7, thiaN kong2 bat ti7 te5-tiam3-a2 cho3 phah-chhiu2. Goa2 toa3 kong-si e5 si5, i tu2-ho2 hou7 kong-si po2 chhut-gak8.....¡¨ ¡§SiaN2-mih? Hou7 lang5 koaiN--koe3 e5 lou5-moa5 oh!¡¨ A-eng siuN7 boe7 kau3 Chhai2-giok8 in e5 ka-teng5 hiah hok8-chap8. ¡§Hit-chun7 kang-te7 phang3-kiN3 thih-kin, a-mou-thou5, kong-si ioh si7 i thong goa7-chhat8 thau chhia khi3 be7--leh, ka7 ko3 khi3 koaiN. Au7--lai5 chha5 chhut-lai5 m7-si7 i, i2-keng peh8 koaiN peh-ko3-goeh8--louh.¡¨ Lim5 chu2-jim7 ke chan7 chit8-ku3: ¡§SiaN2-lang5 kio3 i u7 phaiN2-te2 luh, m7-chiah hou7 lang5 hiam5-gi5 tai7-seng, phaiN2-un7 che7 oan-gak8.¡¨ ¡§An2-ne in bou2 chiah lai5 li7-khui si7--bo5?¡¨ ¡§He m7-si7--nou3, A-hiong chu7 Kheng3-tong5 liah8 khi3 koaiN, taN khi2 ka-teng5 seng-oah8, khi3 li2-sia7 cho3 lu2-tiong than3 chhi7 gin2-a2. Aih! Bai2 to7 bai2 ti7 chia....¡¨ KhoaN3 A-eng thiaN kah hiN7-a2 gia5-gia5-gia5, koh kong2 soa3--loh8-khi3: ¡§Kheng3-tong5 chhut-gak8, m7-chai tui3 toh thiaN--lai5, kong2 A-hiong cho3 lu2-tiong kiam teh than3, ka7 but8 kah toa7-khang se3-lih8. A-hiong sin-khou2 than3 chhi7 chit8-ke, tian-to3 hou7 in ang ka7 tiap8, m7-goan7 chiah lai5 li7-khui chhu3--li2.¡¨ ¡§I gin2-a2 pang3 e7 khui kha?¡¨ ¡§ThiaN kong2 u7 to3-tng2--lai5, m7-koh sui5 koh chau2--khi3. Sui-jian5 Kheng3-tong5 ho7-cho3 ou-to7, iau2 bo5-kau3 ou, sng3 sui2-phoe nia