  Ui3 Lim5 chu2-jim7 hia chai-iaN2 Chhai2-giok8 chi2-moai7 sin-se3, koh khoaN3 hiah che7 keng3-ko3 to5-chhe e5 chhoe7-lang5 khe2-su7, A-eng chhim-chhim kam2-siu7 se3-kan, peng7 m7-si7 chhiuN7 i jit8-siong5 teh siuN7 teh koe3 hiah tan-sun5. Lian5 ang-bou2-ian5, bu2-kiaN2-cheng5 to long2 chhui3 kah e7 khi3 niu2-khiok, siong-hai7--tioh8, piN3 kah chit8-ke-hoe2-a2 soaN3 me5-me5. Na7 an2-ne, Chhai2-giok8 in ai3 an2-choaN2 hou tng2--lai5 a-bu2 e5 ai3--leh? Bun7-te5 e5 kat-thau5 eng3-kai ti7 Kheng3-tong5 hia, na7 khah kut-lat8, khah mi5-noa7 chhoe7, cha-bou2-lang5 e5 sim na2 moa5-chi5--leh, khah an2-choaN2 kam2 boe7 hoe5-sim choan2-i3?
  Koe3 bo5 kui2 kang, A-eng bo5-i3-tiong ti7 lou7--li2 khi3 tu2-tioh8 Chhai2-giok8 in pe7-a2-kiaN2. Hng7-hng7 khoaN3-tioh8 Kheng3-tong5 chiaN3-chhiu2 pho7 se3, to3-chhiu2 khan toa7 kiaN5 oa2--lai5. A-eng it-si5 chhiong-tong7, hoah chit8-siaN: ¡§Oeh! Tan2--chit8-e7.¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 bo5-thau5 bo5-chang2 khi3 hou7 A-eng hoah chit8-siaN, kha-pou7 pang3 tiaN7, bak8-thau5 kat--khi2-lai5: ¡§..SiaN2 tai7-chi3?¡¨ A-eng hoah liau2-au7, chiah ui7-tioh8 toa7-siaN siuN chhong2-pong7 teh hio7-hoe2. Koh khoaN3 se3-han3--e5 soan loh8 thou5-kha, tui3 in lau7-pe7 toa7-thui2 lam2-tiau5-tiau5, toa7--e5 iap bih khi3 in lau7-pe7 e5 kha-chhng au7. ¡§Goa2 soah chhiuN7 chit8-chiah hou2-pah-bu2--leh,¡¨ A-eng siuN7-tioh8 chin au3-nau2, ¡§E7 khi3 hehN-kiaN tioh8 gin2-a2.¡¨ It-si5 in3 boe7--chhut-lai5, ka-chai3 hoan2-eng3 iau2 sng3 ho2: ¡§Goa2 si7 kong2...lin2 sin poaN--lai5, hoan7-se3-a2 e7 khiam3 siaN2, goa2 hia kam2-a2-tiam3, chhai3-ke3-a2, mih8-kiaN7 chiau5 koh pian5-gi5, ....chiah lai5 kau-koan--lah.¡¨ ¡§Goa2 chai-iaN2.¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 chim-chiok siong3 A-eng: ¡§Na7 khiam3, goan2 e7 khi3 be2.¡¨ SiaN bo5 toa7, lioh8-lioh8-a2 chhim-tim5. Hou7 A-eng in3-siong2 siong7 chhim, iau2-si7 chit8 sin ko7 thou5-soa-hun2-a2 e5 khah-ki5 saN-a2-khou3. Chhui3-chhiu bo5 khau, sui-jian5 hou7 lang5 khoaN3-tioh8 boe7 tho2-iah, m7-koh, chit8-sut-a2 to bo5 tian7-iaN2 lai7-te2 ou-sia7-hoe7 ¡§ou-to7¡¨ e5 pa3-khi3. Tian-to3 hou7 A-eng kam2-kak na2 siu7-chin7 hong-song, si3-ke3 chau2-chong5 hit-khoan2 long5-poe7, lok8-phek-khoan2. ¡§Che tai7-khai3 si7 bou2 kou3 boe7 ho2, kou3 boe7-tiau5 e5 cha-pou-lang5-khoan2--lah.¡¨ KhoaN3 kah nng7-e5 se3-han3 gin2-a2 si3-lui2 bak8-chiu iN5-kun3-kun3, A-eng sit8-chai7 siuN7 beh thau5-mng5 ka7 loah-loah8--leh, phiN7 chheng3-chheng3--leh. M7-koh, Kheng3-tong5 chit8-chhiu2 khan chit8-e5, cho3 in kiaN5 chau2--khi3-a-lah.
  Chu7 an2-ne A-eng m7-bat koh khoaN3-kiN3 Chhai2-giok8 in chi2-moai7 lai5 khiok chhai3-hah8-a2. Kheng3-tong5 bat lai5 kau-koan, tai7-pou7-hun7 be2 saN-tng3 chu2-chiah8--e5. A-eng chim-chiok ka7 chu3-i3, m7-bat khoaN3 ka7 gin2-a2 be2 si3-siu3-a2. Kheng3-tong5 ka-ti7 bo5 be2 hun, chiu2, lian5 gin2-a2 e5 chhui3-chiah8-mih8-a2 to long2 khiam7 kah li7-li7, m7-chai in chiN5 khai toh khi3--e5. Au7-lai5 thiaN Lim5 chu2-jim7 kong2, chiah chai-iaN2 Kheng3-tong5 chheng2-tiau3 lai5 Chiang-hoa3, li7 in tau kin7 ho2 chiau3-kou3. Kheng3-tong5 in lau7-pe7, tiuN7-lang5-pa5 si7 toa3 Lam5-tau5 kang7-chng--li2 e5 lang5, chu7 se3-han3 se2 kui2 chap8-ni5 chhiu7-chi5 e5 lau7-peng5-iu2. A-hiong ke3--lai5, Kheng3-tong5 bo5 kou3 ho2 koh khi3 hou7 chau2 bo5 khoaN3--kiN3, hou7 nng7-lau7 khian thau5-khak i bo5 oe7 kong2, ai3 beh tho2-lang5 chiah si7 thau5--thiaN3. Kheng3-tong5 than3 e5 goeh8-kip to7 iong7 ti7 chau2-chhoe7 in A-hiong kap pou2-thiap nng7-lau7 e5 seng-oah8 siong7. Bok8-koai3 Kheng3-tong5 hiah khiu5-khiam7, ka-chai3 gin2-a2 koai, bo5, hoan5 ma7 hoan5--si2.
  E7 khi3 khiu2-kin7 A-eng kap Kheng3-tong5 in pe7-a2-kiaN2, si7 chhiaN3 Chhai2-giok8 au7 e5 tai7-chi3. Kau3 it-kiu2-chhit-kiu2-ni5, A-eng seng-li2 cho3 kah chin bo5-eng5, A-hoe mi7-tiam3 ma7 kang7-khoan2. A-eng e7 ki3--tit, kui2-lo7 ni5 bo5 tng2--lai5 e5 A-pheng5, toa3 bo5 saN-kang koh khi3 Jit8-pun2 liau2-au7. Bo5 joa7 ku2 in lau7-pe7 pak-tou2 to7 hoah thiaN3. Khi2-seng ioh si7 ui7-peN7, i lai5 i khi3, ju2 i ju2 bai2. M7-tiam3 bo5 chai5-tiau7 kou3 bo5 iau3-kin2, koh tioh8-ai3 A-hoe toe3-tiau5-tiau5. Thau5-a2 A-hoe iang Siu3-tin tau3 kou3-tiam3, Siu3-tin bo5 khun3-tau3 the2-lat8 boe7 khan--li, tioh8 thoa A-eng tau3 kou3. A-eng chu7 thau3-cha2 to7 bo5-eng5, chit-ma2 lian5 hioh-chhoan2 to bo5, siuN7-siuN7--leh m7-si7 pan7-hoat, to7 beh chhiaN3 khoaN3 u7 lang5 tau3-saN-kang7--bo5. Mng7 chegn5 mng7 au7 chhiaN3 bo5 lang5, chiah hou7 i siuN7 khi2 Chhai2-giok8. Hit-chun7 Chhai2-giok8 thak8 kok-hau7-a2 saN-ni5, mui2-jit8 thak8 poaN3-kang. A-eng ti7 Kheng3-tong5 lai5 kam2-a2-tiam3 e5 si5 mng7: ¡§Beh hou7 lin2 Chhai2-giok8 than3 chit8-sut-a2 kang-chiN5-a2--bo5?¡¨ KhoaN3 Kheng3-tong5 ti5-tu5: ¡§Hong3-sim, e7 hou7 cho3 i e7-hiau2 cho3 e5 khang-khoe3--lah.¡¨ A-eng hit-chun7 ma7 pun boe7 chheng si7 kin2 ai3 lang5 tau3-kha-chhiu2, ah ah8 si7 u7-sim beh hou7 than3-chiN5-a2-kiaN2. Kau3 thau5 chit8-kang Chhai2-giok8 beh tng2--khi3 si5, A-eng chhek8 chit8-oaN2 mi7 kah chit8-liap8 lou2-nng7, hou7 chiah8 e5 si5 chiah chhoe7-tioh8 tap-an3. Chhai2-giok8 mi7 khng3 thau5-cheng5, kan-taN m7 giah8-ti7, A-eng bak8-chiu thang3 koe3 saN-teng5 piah: ¡§Cho3 li2 chiah8, si7 li2 ka-ti7 than3--e5.¡¨ A-eng chit8-si3-lang5 m7-bat chiah hoaN-hi2: ¡§Goa2 e7 koh chhek8 nng7-oaN2 hou7 li2 theh--tng2, li2 e7-sai2-tit ka7 lin2 lau7-pe7, sio2-moai7 tian2-po2, che si7 li2 cho3 khang-khoe3 than3--lai5-e5-oh.¡¨
  Keng-koe3 A-eng tauh8-tauh8-a2 khan-ka3, Chhai2-giok8 ko3-seng3 chiam7-chiam7 khai-long2--khi2-lai5. U7-iaN2 A-eng kan-taN hou7 cho3 i e7-hiau2 cho3--e5, sui-jian5 an2-ne, ti7 chit saN kham2 tiam3 teh bo5-eng5 e5 lang5, to kam2-kak chha chiok che7. Pi2-lun7-kong2 tiam3 mi7-tian3 tau3-kha-chhiu2, se2-oaN2 phang5-mi7 chio-hou lang5-kheh, A-hoe to7 ke chin khin-sang. A-hoe chhoa7 A-beng5 khi3 khoaN3 peN7 si5, A-eng koe3-lai5 tau3-kha-chhiu2, i to7 koe3-khi3 kam2-a2-tiam3 kou3-tiam3. Sui-jian5 chin che7 tai7-chi3 iau2 boe7-hiau2 cho3, m7-koh, chap8-chap8 tih-tih khang-khoe3, long2 e7 khioh-khioh-a2 cho3. Kui-boe2 m7-na7 A-eng, lian5 Siu3-tin to chin thiaN3-sioh.
  Goan5-pun2 chhiaN3 Chhai2-giok8 si7 chiam7-si5--e5, m7-koh A-beng5 peN7 long2 bo5 ho2. KhoaN3 peN7 tioh8 chiN5, ju2 khai ju2 che7 ju2 an5, peN7-iN7 se3-keng ma7 ju2 khoaN3 ju2 toa7-keng ju2 siong-tiong7. Kau3 boe2--a2 i-seng kong2 koaN-gam5 si5, A-hoe kui-e5 lang5 kiong7 beh pang--khi3. ¡§Kam2 e7-tang3 bak8-chiu kim-kim khoaN3 goan2 A-beng5 teh hoah thiaN3, kio3 kan-khou2?¡¨ A-hoe bin7-iu-bin7-kat: ¡§I-seng kong2 koaN tioh8 that--khi2-lai5, hoan7-se3-a2 iau2 u7 kiu3.¡¨ Siu3-tin chit8-e7 thiaN an2-ne kong2, kio3 Jit8-seng chhoan5 chap8-ban7-khou, kiu3 lang5 iau3-kin2. Mia7 kiu3--si7 kiu3--tioh8, kho2-sioh thoa--nia5, hoan tng2-ni5, iau2-si7 tng2--khi3-a-lah.
  Hit-tang-chun7, A-eng khoaN3 A-hoe ui7-tioh8 A-beng5 e5 ioh8-hui3 teh chau2-chong5, sim-cheng5 ma7 toe3 i ut-bun7. ThiaN Siu3-tin kong2 A-beng5 beh chiong hou7-leng5-a2 ku7-chhu3 koe3--koe3-lai5, Jit8-seng khou2-chhio3: ¡§Sui5-chai7--i-lah, chioh--i e5 chiN5, pun2-chiaN5 to7 bo5 beh tho2 tng2--lai5.¡¨ Lun7-chin kong2 chhu3-khak bo5 tat8-chiN5, thou2-te7 kek8-ke ma7 chiah chap8-ban7-khou nia5. A-eng chai-iaN2 A-hoe i2-keng chioh ji7-chap8 goa7-goa7 ban7, ¡§Bo5 chioh--i, si7 beh an2-choaN2?¡¨ Jit8-seng kong2-tioh8 chin bu5-nai7. Sit8-chai7, A-hoe u7 chiN5 chioh kah bo5 chiN5, u7 lou7 kiaN5 kah bo5 lou7. A-eng eng2-oan2 to e7 ki3--tit, chit8-kang, A-chiong khi3 in saN-chi2 hia chioh bo5 chiN5 tng2--lai5: ¡§A-siam5 kong2 choe3-kin7 an5-tong3-tong3, leng7-kang chhiu2-thau5 khah leng7--leh, e7 kia3--lai5.¡¨ A-hoe thiaN kong2, ia7 bo5 in3 to7 oat jip8-khi3 lai7-te2. Oa2 mng5-thau5-a2, hiong5-hiong5 kui-khou-lang5 oat8 to3--koe3-lai5: ¡§An5? Ke3 kui chap8-ni5--a, teh hoah an5?¡¨ A-eng khoaN3 A-hoe oat8 chit8-e7 siuN kin2, thau5-mng5 sam3 kah am kui-bin7: ¡§...Iau2-boe7 leng7-hou3-hou3? ....Kui2 beh sin3!¡¨ A-eng bo5-tiuN bo5-ti5 kui seng-khu khi2 ka-nng2-sun2. Lang5 kong2 ku2-peN7 bo5 hau3-chu2, bu2-kiaN2-cheng5 kiaN5 kah chit-khoan2 te7-pou7, chin-chin si7...., aih!
